    <p class="heading_space"><a name="requirements" class="heading" id="deadlink">What do I need to use the plugin?</a></p>
    <p>You'll need:</p>
    <ul class="specific">
      <li class="specific">A self-hosted <a href="http://wordpress.org/" class="specific_link">Wordpress</a> blog. Placeling doesn't yet work on Wordpress.com (If you're a Wordpress.com blogger, please take a moment to <a href="http://en.support.wordpress.com/plugins/" class="specific_link">request that they add us</a>)</li>
